Product description

Meta Fundamentals 15000 Women's 33" Labcoat

Meta Fundamentals

A great value for groups, Meta Fundamentals styles combine function with the utmost in labcoat value.

  • Great for groups
  • Style and function
  • Soil Release

GREAT COATS FOR GROUPS

This labcoat features a four-button closure, two lower pockets, chest pocket with pencil pocket stitch, and a one-piece back.

  • 65% Polyester, 35% Cotton Poplin with Soil Release
  • Four-button front closure
  • Two lower pockets
  • One chest pocket with pencil pocket stitch
  • One-piece back
  • Sizes: XXS-5X
